name: Toshocat
description: Track and Discover your favorite Anime and Manga on your desktop

releases.body:
- Fixes window not closing when quitting through tray (again)
- Added new "Reload Toshocat" action in the top-left menu

- Fix Toshocat not quitting properly on update
- Update `react-collapse` and `react-height` deps.
- Add new featured series for summer 2016

- Fix Toshocat mascot not showing in updater window
- Update window is not always on top anymore

- Fix Calendar styling
- Make app updater more reliable
- Fix Toshocat not properly quitting

- Update syncer messages
- Auto updater now checks for updates every hour
- Add +1 progress button
- Fix main window not showing up properly  on startup

- Fix app not properly syncing with service on launch
- Fix scrobbler failing to update MAL list if series already existed in list

- Auto updater now pops up as a window when there is a new update installing
- Sortable list headers
- Possible to have a 1-10 rating
Media detection now works in prod as well
